---
title: Pesto & Parmesan Venison-Beef Meatballs with Veggie-Loaded Tomato Sauce & Creamy Mash
description: Change what you know about meatballs by adding a dollop of basil pesto to your mixture for an easy way to add flavour and
unbeatable texture. Served with a simple tomato sauce alongside creamy mash potato (and we haven’t forgotten cheese!),
this is an Italian-inspired bowl that all will love!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pesto-parmesan-beef-venison-meatballs-7e85620e.jpg
